{"tid":2215181,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"武漢肺炎｜內地大學生被關宿舍情緒爆發 集體大叫「解封」半小時","createTime":"2020-09-23T21:33:00.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-24T04:21:38.000Z","uid":130626,"like":9,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"99ac0b66cffb31461ce1c589fef4f6260b2832d0","tid":2215181,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:33:00.000Z","msg":"內地大學生在疫後開課，卻躁動不安，事關校園仍然實施防疫封閉式管理，但校方又管理不善，導致學生集體緒情大爆發，近日不斷出現抗議聲音。其中，陝西西安外國語大學的學生因不滿長期封校令生活嚴重受影響，再加上校內超市坐地起價、出售過期食物，日前在宿舍內大叫「解封」半小時。另外，四川傳媒學院的保安人員，在封校期間竟將商販速遞到校園的外賣扔掉，因而與學生發生衝突。校方最後出面調停，才未有令事件惡化。<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200924/DIBTOHVITJCQXHIGZP7L6H3SD4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200924%2FDIBTOHVITJCQXHIGZP7L6H3SD4%2F&d=NOH35fHRfA96o6n45SGJFAu0mcv%2FJYK%2F5hhNgdoT3Fo%3D&h=0997c3c8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200924%2FDIBTOHVITJCQXHIGZP7L6H3SD4%2F&h=e89809ea\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200924/DIBTOHVITJCQXHIGZP7L6H3SD4/</a>"},{"pid":"75cab8ea336af040b20677928f7542d39190d676","tid":2215181,"uid":12609,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:35:09.000Z","msg":"想搞安獨？支持公安嚴正執法！"},{"pid":"ad1307d626ef0bb196b09264fd845d660b570402","tid":2215181,"uid":359022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:58:12.000Z","msg":"呢個時候如果知更鳥係度一定會講：一把火燒"},{"pid":"d7c081b6169878c7188aad8c1b50aee43895e6ba","tid":2215181,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"75cab8ea336af040b20677928f7542d39190d676","tid":2215181,"uid":12609,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T21:35:09.000Z","msg":"想搞安獨？支持公安嚴正執法！"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T22:03:10.000Z","msg":"西毒"},{"pid":"da0fa2221df9173e6ae10193b38a4eaa395c0571","tid":2215181,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-23T22:08:54.000Z","msg":"西安學生